{"tid":2302622,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「動物天橋」有用！牠們都走這穿越公路","createTime":"2020-11-27T09:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T14:02:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"930d7a8e24ff03bfdea5e89925c15fa0e0a68b35","tid":2302622,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/11/27/realtime/9150980.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2Frealtime%2F9150980.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=d34bc613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n猶他州野生動植物資源局在80號州際公路上建造了這座「動物天橋」，以減少野生動物在帕雷峽谷造成的交通事故，成效顯著。FACEBOOK／Utah Division of Wildlife Resources<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為了避免野生動物穿越繁忙高速公路發生意外，美國猶他州（Utah）官員想到一個好點子，就是為動物們在高速公路上建造一座「動物天橋」，官方最新的影片也顯示這項計畫效果顯著。<br />\n<br />\n猶他州野生動植物資源局（Utah Division of Wildlife Resources）在80號州際公路上建造了這座「動物天橋」，20日在臉書上發布了各種野生動物「妥善利用」這座天橋的影片，可以見到包括麋鹿、豪豬和鹿，甚至連熊都走這個天橋來穿越高速公路，官方興奮地說：「它起作用了！」<br />\n<br />\n這座天橋約106公尺長、耗資500萬美元打造，於2018年12月開放，是該州首座動物用天橋。上面擺滿了岩石、巨石和原木營造出野外氛圍藉此吸引動物。<br />\n<br />\n猶他州交通局發言人格里森（John Gleason）2019年曾向鹽湖論壇報（Salt Lake Tribune）表示，動物利用天橋的早期成果良好，儘管牠們要完全習慣仍需幾年時間，但自從天橋設立以來，當地的事故量大大減少，代表這項投資收到回報。<br />\n<br />\n看片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UtahDWR/videos/3416838815036581/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUtahDWR%2Fvideos%2F3416838815036581%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=bee9bff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UtahDWR/videos/3416838815036581/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/11/27/realtime/9150981.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2Frealtime%2F9150981.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=36e089b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各式各樣的野生動物都利用這座「動物天橋」穿越高速公路，包括麋鹿、豪豬和鹿，甚至連熊都妥善利用。FACEBOOK／Utah Division of Wildlife Resources<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7470/5048269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7470%2F5048269&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=3fbcad1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7470/5048269</a>"},{"pid":"af456be91652aa73ad256adb1cfaed227e50f47b","tid":2302622,"uid":12628,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"好過元朗咩用幾億起條橋比班鄉黑去拜山"},{"pid":"53f555b2e07f724ee5f8ebb3ae1acd64d462d491","tid":2302622,"uid":66365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"打獵或者啲肉食動物cam 死喺到咪好撚屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e791bcbfe8b814b34c4debab45c0afc1a869e74","tid":2302622,"uid":11067,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港動物天橋代表"},{"pid":"390842aea1e5521cfc368713d74d5d853bdd8b26","tid":2302622,"uid":137038,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:17:33.000Z","msg":"動物通道其實香港都有，例如西鐵元朗段近東頭村，仲有大欖隧道汀九入口，不過就無乜動物用<br />\n大埔道可以嘅話最好就起多條天橋畀馬騮過馬路"},{"pid":"9e9288c934a1dfdfd6cbbc58ca002d917d824244","tid":2302622,"uid":193642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"53f555b2e07f724ee5f8ebb3ae1acd64d462d491","tid":2302622,"uid":66365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11